<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/about.css">
<body>
    <div class="title">
        <h1><img class="logo" src="/images/logo.png" alt="logo"></h1>
        <%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>
    </div>

    <div class="about-container">

       
        <div class="about-hero">
            <div class="about-hero-text">
                <p class="about-tag">Est. Thamel, Kathmandu</p>
                <h1 class="about-title">Your ride through <span class="about-title-green">Kathmandu</span> starts here</h1>
                <p class="about-desc">Bike Rental Thamel is your go-to destination for affordable and reliable bike rentals in the heart of Kathmandu — from the busy streets of Thamel to trails leading to Nagarkot and Bhaktapur.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-stats">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <p class="stat-number">50+</p>
                    <p class="stat-label">Bikes available</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <p class="stat-number">7</p>
                    <p class="stat-label">Days a week</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <p class="stat-number">3</p>
                    <p class="stat-label">Rental plans</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <p class="stat-number">4★</p>
                    <p class="stat-label">Avg. rating</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <p class="section-label">Why choose us</p>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3 class="feature-title">Well Maintained</h3>
                <p class="feature-desc">Every bike is regularly serviced to ensure your safety and comfort on any road.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3 class="feature-title">Flexible Plans</h3>
                <p class="feature-desc">Hourly, daily, and weekly rentals so you can explore at your own pace.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3 class="feature-title">Friendly Staff</h3>
                <p class="feature-desc">Our team helps you pick the right bike and suggests the best routes around the valley.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

     
        <p class="section-label">Our fleet</p>
        <div class="fleet-grid">
            <div class="fleet-card">
                <p class="fleet-name">City Bikes</p>
                <p class="fleet-desc">Casual rides around Thamel and Kathmandu</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-card">
                <p class="fleet-name">Mountain Bikes</p>
                <p class="fleet-desc">Off-road trails and hilly terrain</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-card">
                <p class="fleet-name">Electric Bikes</p>
                <p class="fleet-desc">Eco-friendly and great for longer distances</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-card">
                <p class="fleet-name">Kids Bikes</p>
                <p class="fleet-desc">Safe and fun for the little explorers</p>
            </div>
        </div>

       
        <p class="section-label">Our commitment</p>
        <div class="commitment-box">
            <p>At Bike Rental Thamel, customer satisfaction is our top priority. We provide clean, well-maintained bikes at the best prices while promoting sustainable and eco-friendly travel.</p>
            <p>Come visit us at Thamel, Kathmandu — we are open 7 days a week and ready to help you start your next adventure!</p>
            <p class="open-badge">Open 7 days a week</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>
